name: \'No of Pipelines\' AS `KPI`
datasource: `app_org` AS `project` FROM `mlfederatedmodels` GROUP BY `app_org` \\nUNION SELECT \'AIP\' AS `module`
alias: `app_org` AS `project` FROM `mlfederatedendpoints` GROUP BY `app_org`\\n UNION SELECT \'AIP\' AS `module`
is_permission_managed: `organization` AS `project` FROM `mlapps` GROUP BY `organization` \\n UNION SELECT \'AIP\' AS `module`
is_archival_enabled: `organization` AS `project` FROM `mladapters` GROUP BY `organization` \\n UNION SELECT \'AIP\' AS `module`
metadata: `organization` AS `project` FROM `mldataset` GROUP BY `organization` \\n UNION SELECT \'AIP\' AS `module`
taskdetails: `organization` AS `project` FROM `mldatasource` GROUP BY `organization` \\n UNION SELECT \'AIP\' AS `module`
adaptername: `organization` AS `project` FROM `mljobs` GROUP BY `organization`\\n) t JOIN usm_project p ON t.project = p.name WHERE p.id= {projectId} GROUP BY module
